02:22.068 --> 02:24.738
Those things are magic. I can't get enough.

02:26.138 --> 02:28.653
Daphne and I have a few
traditions of our own.

02:28.653 --> 02:31.716
We like to go to a movie on Christmas,
sneak in some Chinese take-out.

02:31.726 --> 02:33.930
Now that sounds like fun. I'm in!

02:34.131 --> 02:37.400
Wait. That's when we do Kennish karaoke.

02:37.434 --> 02:39.244
<i>You know, in the afternoon.</i>

02:39.271 --> 02:41.960
Maybe we could do a movie on the 26th.

02:42.080 --> 02:44.240
Daphne can't really do karaoke...

02:44.274 --> 02:46.058
It's okay. I don't mind.

02:46.067 --> 02:48.600
... And I hate to sing,
so I think maybe we're out.

02:49.771 --> 02:52.588
Mom, it's okay to shake
things up a little bit.

02:52.588 --> 02:54.164
I don't think it's too much to ask

02:54.170 --> 02:56.452
