03:11.949 --> 03:13.431
Regina...

03:16.476 --> 03:19.540
I don't get it. What does Chinese
food have to do with Christmas?

03:19.586 --> 03:21.442
<i>Bay: Come on, mom. What is with you?</i>

03:21.470 --> 03:22.676
You're like a cruise director

03:22.677 --> 03:23.979
