03:40.074 --> 03:42.498
Why can't we have that just one time?

03:43.952 --> 03:45.616
You know what?

03:46.257 --> 03:47.500
You can.

03:47.620 --> 03:49.438
Have a good time with the Kennishes.

03:50.540 --> 03:52.184
Mom!

03:54.735 --> 03:56.912
Well, that was a disaster.

03:56.930 --> 03:58.549
Tell me about it.

03:59.729 --> 04:01.714
One last garlic knot.

04:01.933 --> 04:03.534
You girls want it?

04:06.443 --> 04:08.154
Split it?

04:09.279 --> 04:10.726
