12:06.653 --> 12:09.450
What's the deal? I
mean, do we go with this?

12:09.487 --> 12:11.289
Or should we tell someone?

12:11.316 --> 12:13.233
Maybe see a doctor? I don't know.

12:13.556 --> 12:17.014
Well, the thing is
apparently, I have a show

12:17.038 --> 12:18.989
